validation.body:
Hi {buyerName},

Your e-invoice {invoiceNumber} from {businessName} has been validated by LHDN Malaysia.

Document UUID: {uuid}
Validation Date: {validatedAt}
Amount: {currency} {totalAmount}

View on MyInvois: https://myinvois.hasil.gov.my/{longId}/share

This is an automated notification from {businessName} via Groot Finance.

